8
00:01:45,719 --> 00:01:48,480
They're move-in ready upon handover.

9
00:01:48,719 --> 00:01:50,280
So this isn't a hidden price hike, is it?

10
00:01:50,760 --> 00:01:51,480
Not at all.

11
00:01:51,480 --> 00:01:52,719
The unit price stays the same.

12
00:01:52,959 --> 00:01:55,280
The finishing comes free with the home.

13
00:01:55,840 --> 00:01:56,760
All our promises

14
00:01:56,760 --> 00:01:57,760
