20
00:02:02,719 --> 00:02:03,239
Wonderful.

21
00:02:03,239 --> 00:02:04,159
Thank you for the referral.

22
00:02:04,400 --> 00:02:06,480
If your referral closes a deal,

23
00:02:07,760 --> 00:02:08,800
