25
00:02:10,759 --> 00:02:11,439
Wow, what a great deal.

26
00:02:12,080 --> 00:02:13,080
Let's go check out the show unit.

27
00:02:13,439 --> 00:02:13,879
If it's suitable,

28
00:02:14,080 --> 00:02:15,159
