34
00:02:41,520 --> 00:02:42,840
Fang Bing's in trouble.

35
00:02:42,840 --> 00:02:44,800
Shouldn't you hurry and hire a lawyer for him?

36
00:02:44,800 --> 00:02:46,360
Who are you dressing up for?

37
00:02:46,879 --> 00:02:48,360
Fang Bing already has a lawyer arranged.

38
00:02:48,599 --> 00:02:50,599
I'm here to discuss the repayment plan.

39
00:02:51,159 --> 00:02:51,879
Repayment?

40
00:02:52,439 --> 00:02:53,360
You've got money now?

41
00:03:10,319 --> 00:03:11,599
Are you serious?

42
00:03:12,680 --> 00:03:13,159
Aunt.

43
00:03:13,639 --> 00:03:15,280
I understand you have your difficulties.

44
00:03:15,800 --> 00:03:17,120
But this repayment plan

45
00:03:17,120 --> 00:03:18,639
has absolutely no issues.

46
00:03:18,879 --> 00:03:19,960
Please trust me.

47
00:03:24,319 --> 00:03:24,960
Yuanyuan.

48
00:03:25,840 --> 00:03:26,879
A while back,

49
00:03:27,319 --> 00:03:28,759
