52
00:03:35,039 --> 00:03:35,800
Aunt.

53
00:03:36,919 --> 00:03:38,000
I've figured things out now.

54
00:03:38,479 --> 00:03:40,080
Life is meant to be lived for yourself.

55
00:03:40,800 --> 00:03:42,280
Once Fang Bing's sentence is handed down,

56
00:03:42,280 --> 00:03:43,159
I'll file for divorce.

57
00:03:43,919 --> 00:03:45,319
Just don't blame me when that time comes.

58
00:03:45,800 --> 00:03:46,439
Ah,

59
00:03:47,080 --> 00:03:48,560
that boy Fang Bing is such a disappointment.

60
00:03:49,199 --> 00:03:50,599
Your life is your own to live.

61
00:03:50,960 --> 00:03:51,800
Divorce him if you must.

62
00:03:52,280 --> 00:03:53,080
Aunt has no objections.

63
00:03:54,599 --> 00:03:55,400
Thank you for understanding.

64
00:03:56,280 --> 00:03:57,120
Then please,

65
00:03:57,400 --> 00:03:58,199
once you've signed and stamped it,

66
00:03:58,520 --> 00:03:59,599
have someone deliver it to me.

67
00:04:02,039 --> 00:04:02,599
Yuanyuan.

68
00:04:03,039 --> 00:04:03,479
Come here.

69
00:04:04,039 --> 00:04:04,879
Let Aunt ask you something.

70
00:04:06,840 --> 00:04:07,840
Lately,

71
00:04:08,360 --> 00:04:10,159
