72
00:04:12,400 --> 00:04:13,479
Aunt, I still have things to do.

73
00:04:13,479 --> 00:04:14,199
I'm leaving now.

74
00:04:28,079 --> 00:04:29,000
A gym,

75
00:04:29,360 --> 00:04:30,519
