76
00:04:30,519 --> 00:04:31,160
Sure, no problem.

77
00:04:31,879 --> 00:04:32,800
Let's look at this one too.

78
00:04:38,600 --> 00:04:39,759
Mr. Xiao.

79
00:04:39,759 --> 00:04:42,079
Wanhe Mansion Phase Two is about to sell out.

80
00:04:42,240 --> 00:04:44,120
For Plot 7 Phase One General Contracting,

81
00:04:44,120 --> 00:04:45,800
