82
00:04:46,319 --> 00:04:46,920
Thank you.

83
00:04:52,079 --> 00:04:52,920
Come.

84
00:04:53,439 --> 00:04:54,199
Let's look at this one.

85
00:04:54,199 --> 00:04:54,600
Mm.

86
00:04:56,040 --> 00:04:57,199
Take this,

87
00:04:57,959 --> 00:04:58,639
this spot here.

88
00:04:59,000 --> 00:05:00,439
Today's meeting topic

89
00:05:00,439 --> 00:05:01,800
is about Plot 7,

90
00:05:01,800 --> 00:05:03,600
the feasibility of developing it as a cultural tourism project.

91
00:05:04,000 --> 00:05:04,680
Xiao Yifan,

92
00:05:05,199 --> 00:05:06,399
present your research report

93
00:05:06,399 --> 00:05:07,319
to everyone.

94
00:05:07,639 --> 00:05:08,600
Yes, Chairman Zheng.

95
00:05:12,480 --> 00:05:13,560
Let's take a look.

96
00:05:13,560 --> 00:05:15,519
I've divided this research report into

97
00:05:15,519 --> 00:05:16,720
