98
00:05:16,720 --> 00:05:17,959
It's very clear and straightforward.

99
00:05:18,480 --> 00:05:19,439
Let's start from page one.

100
00:05:19,879 --> 00:05:22,040
The project background and plot overview.

101
00:05:22,519 --> 00:05:23,600
Let's take a look.

102
00:05:23,600 --> 00:05:27,040
Our background is based on national support for the cultural tourism industry,

103
00:05:27,240 --> 00:05:30,240
within Loujiang City's strategic plan,

104
00:05:30,240 --> 00:05:33,079
and the surrounding natural resources are exceptionally rich.

105
00:05:33,079 --> 00:05:35,560
Phase One sold extremely well.

106
00:05:35,560 --> 00:05:37,560
And our brand and customer trust

107
00:05:37,560 --> 00:05:38,920
have been very firmly established.

108
00:05:38,920 --> 00:05:40,879
Let's take a look at our...

109
00:05:40,879 --> 00:05:43,279
The group received a whistleblower letter.

110
00:05:43,959 --> 00:05:45,519
Why is there still no action?

111
00:05:51,839 --> 00:05:53,399
Show this contract to the client.

112
00:05:53,600 --> 00:05:54,600
Yes, Ms. Su.

113
00:06:18,839 --> 00:06:22,040
The cultural tourism project for Plot 7 Phase Two

114
00:06:22,040 --> 00:06:23,040
is basically confirmed.

115
00:06:23,879 --> 00:06:24,360
Han Lin,

116
00:06:24,759 --> 00:06:26,079
don't call me anymore.

117
00:06:26,639 --> 00:06:28,079
At Taihe Sales Agency,

118
00:06:28,079 --> 00:06:29,439
we do business based on merit.

119
00:06:29,839 --> 00:06:31,000
We don't resort to shady tactics.

120
00:06:32,199 --> 00:06:32,800
Su Yuanyuan,

121
00:06:33,199 --> 00:06:34,319
