122
00:06:34,959 --> 00:06:36,639
Haven't I tipped you off enough times?

123
00:06:36,959 --> 00:06:38,720
You egged Fang Bing on to falsify things

124
00:06:38,720 --> 00:06:39,879
and took kickbacks from me.

125
00:06:40,279 --> 00:06:41,399
You're devious,

126
00:06:41,399 --> 00:06:42,800
and now you're pinning it on others.

127
00:06:43,680 --> 00:06:45,319
Sooner or later, your selfish greed

128
00:06:45,600 --> 00:06:46,759
will get you the punishment you deserve.

129
00:06:47,079 --> 00:06:47,920
Su Yuanyuan,

130
00:06:48,360 --> 00:06:50,040
