131
00:06:51,720 --> 00:06:52,639
Listen to me—

132
00:06:58,519 --> 00:06:59,040
Hello?

133
00:06:59,759 --> 00:07:00,199
Hello?

134
00:07:34,000 --> 00:07:34,839
Assistant Han.

135
00:07:38,800 --> 00:07:39,600
You needed something?

136
00:07:40,439 --> 00:07:40,759
Mr. Xiao.

137
00:07:43,120 --> 00:07:44,519
Chairman Zheng sent me to ask

138
00:07:44,959 --> 00:07:46,480
about the General Contracting for Plot 7.

139
00:07:47,160 --> 00:07:49,360
Which firms made the Bidding shortlist?

140
00:07:51,040 --> 00:07:52,680
Did Chairman Zheng really send you?

141
00:07:53,839 --> 00:07:54,680
What's that supposed to mean?

142
00:07:56,639 --> 00:07:58,560
He Junjie's team is still evaluating.

143
00:07:59,279 --> 00:08:00,720
The Bidding meeting will be held in due course.

144
00:08:01,560 --> 00:08:03,680
Everything is on schedule.

145
00:08:05,920 --> 00:08:08,240
Why are you in such a rush?

146
00:08:10,240 --> 00:08:10,879
Mr. Xiao.

147
00:08:11,439 --> 00:08:12,959
What are you implying?

148
00:08:13,560 --> 00:08:17,160
Chairman Zheng just feels that for Plot 7 Phase One's General Contracting,

149
00:08:17,720 --> 00:08:19,000
the Bidding is taking a bit too long.

150
00:08:19,639 --> 00:08:21,160
He merely asked me to check in.

151
00:08:24,079 --> 00:08:27,040
If there's an issue, I'll report to Chairman Zheng myself.

152
00:08:28,040 --> 00:08:28,879
Assistant

153
00:08:30,079 --> 00:08:30,800
Han.

154
00:08:31,800 --> 00:08:33,559
The company has its chain of authority.

155
00:08:34,000 --> 00:08:35,480
Know your place.

156
00:08:36,200 --> 00:08:37,159
Don't ask questions

157
00:08:37,679 --> 00:08:38,399
you shouldn't be asking.

158
00:08:38,919 --> 00:08:41,000
Xiao Yifan, don't push it.

159
00:08:41,720 --> 00:08:43,200
When I was Chairman Zheng's assistant,

160
00:08:43,200 --> 00:08:44,240
