161
00:08:44,720 --> 00:08:46,360
What right do you have to be so arrogant in front of me?

162
00:08:47,000 --> 00:08:47,840
Assistant Han.

163
00:08:48,240 --> 00:08:50,600
I'm just following company policy.

164
00:08:51,000 --> 00:08:52,000
Xiao Yifan.

165
00:08:52,279 --> 00:08:53,759
Don't push it.

166
00:08:55,279 --> 00:08:56,440
How am I pushing it?

167
00:08:56,879 --> 00:08:57,639
How about this,

168
00:08:58,399 --> 00:09:00,879
let's call Chairman Zheng right now

169
00:09:01,279 --> 00:09:03,399
and see if he really sent you to ask.

170
00:09:04,240 --> 00:09:05,399
Fine.

171
00:09:06,159 --> 00:09:07,519
Just you wait.

172
00:09:13,039 --> 00:09:13,840
Chairman Zheng.

173
00:09:14,240 --> 00:09:15,639
We've obtained evidence

174
00:09:15,639 --> 00:09:16,480
of Han Lin taking bribes.

175
00:09:16,879 --> 00:09:18,200
If there are no objections,

176
00:09:18,200 --> 00:09:19,399
we will

177
00:09:19,600 --> 00:09:22,120
use the leaking of major corporate trade secrets

178
00:09:22,120 --> 00:09:22,840
as grounds to sue Han Lin.

179
00:09:26,320 --> 00:09:27,200
You can guard against everything,

180
00:09:28,080 --> 00:09:28,960
but not a thief from within.

181
00:09:29,639 --> 00:09:30,120
Chairman Zheng.

182
00:09:30,519 --> 00:09:31,639
Should we detain Han Lin?

183
00:09:34,960 --> 00:09:36,200
Follow the proper procedures.

184
00:09:36,320 --> 00:09:37,759
Yes, understood.

185
00:09:55,279 --> 00:09:56,480
Since joining the company,

186
00:09:56,480 --> 00:10:00,240
I've been deeply honored by the trust and care from my leaders and colleagues.

187
00:10:01,080 --> 00:10:02,480
I'm deeply grateful.

188
00:10:03,799 --> 00:10:05,399
Due to personal family reasons,

189
00:10:05,720 --> 00:10:07,360
after careful consideration,

190
00:10:07,360 --> 00:10:09,679
I hereby formally submit my resignation.

191
00:10:10,120 --> 00:10:12,480
For any inconvenience caused,

192
00:10:12,480 --> 00:10:14,080
I sincerely apologize.

193
00:10:15,519 --> 00:10:17,799
Please grant your approval.

194
00:10:18,519 --> 00:10:20,879
I wish all leaders and colleagues

195
00:10:20,879 --> 00:10:22,240
good health,

196
00:10:22,360 --> 00:10:24,000
and continued success.

197
00:10:40,639 --> 00:10:41,960
Twenty years of hard work

198
00:10:44,159 --> 00:10:45,720
just ends like this.

199
00:11:33,519 --> 00:11:34,519
Please, have some tea.

200
00:11:34,919 --> 00:11:36,240
Is there anything else you'd like to say?

201
00:11:38,879 --> 00:11:39,639
Chairman Zheng.

202
00:11:40,159 --> 00:11:41,480
This is my resignation letter.

203
00:11:41,600 --> 00:11:44,080
I'm no longer fit to stay at the company.

204
00:11:44,679 --> 00:11:45,840
Please, show me some mercy.

205
00:11:46,120 --> 00:11:46,679
Just let me go.
